          <ul>
            <li><i class="bx bx-check"></i> Backend Software Engineering (Java, .NET, Cobol</li>
            <li><i class="bx bx-check"></i> Frontend Software Engineering (HTML/CSS, React, Vue, Angular, RoR)</li>
